<chapter line="1">Vetullavādassa paṭhamaniggaho</chapter>
<paragraph line="2"><bold></bold><bold></bold><note>nikāyasaṅgahe 12-piṭṭhe</note>. Vuttañhetaṃ mahāvaṃse –</paragraph>
<hangnum line="3" number="36-41"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="4">‘‘Vetullavādaṃ madditvā, kāretvā pāpaniggahaṃ;</gatha1>
<gathalast line="5">Kapilena amaccena, sāsanaṃ jotayī ca so’’ti.</gathalast>
